      "plain": "TL;DR: This section lists serious offenses and minimum consequences. “Minimum” matters: administrators may increase consequences depending on severity, circumstances, and prior record. Some incidents may involve suspension, expulsion, law enforcement, or the district’s canine detection program.",
      "student": "Do not use this section as a consequence menu. The listed consequences are minimums, and the school can respond more seriously depending on what happened. Weapons, drugs/alcohol, fighting, threats, harassment, and major disruption can have serious outcomes.",
