      "plain": "TL;DR: This section covers student sexual harassment protections and bus safety expectations. Students should report harassment, and bus riders must follow safety rules so transportation remains safe for everyone.",
      "student": "If harassment happens, report it to a trusted adult or administrator. On the bus, follow the driver, stay seated, keep aisles clear, keep hands/items to yourself, and avoid behavior that distracts the driver or creates safety problems.",
